data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home is located in Von Dales community.  It is convenient to interstate access, just minutes from center point parkway.  It has a spacious open split level floor plan.  The kitchen has been upgraded with stainless steel appliances.  New refrigrator and oven.  3 bedrooms and full bath on main level with beautiful hardwood floors.  Partial basement and half bath downstairs with laminate flooring.  Your basement is a great area for entertaining family/friends our just relaxation.  Then walk outside to your back yard oasis that has 2 storage sheds.  Park your car in the garage or in your personal driveway. Owners have kept the house in meticulous shape.  Come see for yourself today and schedule a showing in showtime.
